Had an enriching experience attending the Adya session yesterday вүЎЖ’ГңГҮ
The session provided a deep dive into AdyaО“ГҮГ–s Agent Studio, a powerful low-code platform designed to build AI agents and intelligent workflows with ease. We explored how AI agents can be visually designed using flow-based components such as Chat Input, Twilio SMS Provider, and Custom Outputs, enabling seamless communication and automation without heavy coding.
What stood out was how Adya simplifies complex AI integrationsО“ГҮГ¶allowing developers and businesses to quickly deploy scalable, real-world solutions like SMS-based interactions, automated responses, and intelligent decision flows. The hands-on walkthrough made it clear how Agent Studio can accelerate development while maintaining flexibility and control.
Overall, it was a great learning opportunity that highlighted the future of AI-driven automation, no-code/low-code development, and practical enterprise use cases. Looking forward to applying these insights and building impactful AI agents using AdyaО“ГҮГ–s platform.
